OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772528658
OL,3,CQatar gas shutdown sends market price
OL,4,Csurging and could impact UK energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FQatarEnergy, the world's largest
OL,8,Fproducer of liquefied natural gas
OL,9,F(LNG), has halted production in a move
OL,10,Fthat has already sent global gas
OL,11,Fprices soaring - and could eventually
OL,12,Ffeed through to the energy bills paid
OL,13,Fby households and businesses in the UK.
OL,15,FThe company's huge Ras Laffan facility
OL,16,Fin Qatar has been targeted by Iranian
OL,17,Fdrone strikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772528658
OL,3,CQatar gas shutdown sends market price
OL,4,Csurging and could impact UK energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FThere is no indication the plant
OL,8,Fitself has been damaged; indeed, the
OL,9,Fshutdown appears to be linked as much
OL,10,Fto disruption in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,11,Fas to any direct hit.
OL,13,FThe strait - one of the world's most
OL,14,Fimportant shipping routes for oil and
OL,15,Fgas - remains open.
OL,17,FBut vessels have been avoiding it
OL,18,Fafter insurers warned they could
OL,19,Fcancel cover or sharply raise premiums
OL,20,Fbecause of the risk of attack.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772528658
OL,3,CQatar gas shutdown sends market price
OL,4,Csurging and could impact UK energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FThat has created a bottleneck.
OL,9,FEmpty tankers cannot get back to Qatar
OL,10,For the UAE - another major LNG
OL,11,Fproducer - to reload, while full
OL,12,Ftankers are waiting offshore with
OL,13,Fnowhere safe to go.
OL,15,FThe result has been an immediate jump
OL,16,Fin prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772528658
OL,3,CQatar gas shutdown sends market price
OL,4,Csurging and could impact UK energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FThe European benchmark gas price,
OL,8,Fknown as TTF, surged by 38% to around
OL,9,FE45 per megawatt hour - the biggest
OL,10,Fdaily move in four years, although
OL,11,Fstill well below the extreme levels
OL,12,Fseen in August 2022 when Vladimir
OL,13,FPutin cut off most Russian supplies to
OL,14,FEurope.
OL,26,@qD@AOk
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772528658
OL,3,CQatar gas shutdown sends market price
OL,4,Csurging and could impact UK energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FThe disruption is bad news for Qatar,
OL,8,Fwhose economy depends heavily on LNG
OL,9,Fexports, but it is also a serious
OL,10,Fconcern for big buyers in Asia,
OL,11,Fincluding India, China, and Japan,
OL,12,Fwhich rely on Qatari gas to keep their
OL,13,Feconomies running.
OL,15,FThe UK does not buy much gas directly
OL,16,Ffrom Qatar. Most of what we use comes
OL,17,Fby pipeline from Norway or as LNG
OL,18,Fshipped from the United States.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772528658
OL,3,CQatar gas shutdown sends market price
OL,4,Csurging and could impact UK energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FBut in a global market, the price is
OL,8,Fset internationally. If Asian buyers
OL,9,Fstart competing more aggressively for
OL,10,Fcargoes that would otherwise have come
OL,11,Fto Europe, prices here can rise even
OL,12,Fif our physical supply does not change.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
