OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772528658
OL,3,CQatar gas shutdown sends market price
OL,4,Csurging and could impact UK energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,F"(The QatarEnergy shutdown) is very,
OL,8,Fvery significant," says Laura Page,
OL,9,FInsight Manager for LNG and natural
OL,10,Fgas at Kpler.
OL,12,F"The key point is that we are still in
OL,13,Fwinter. We haven't yet reached the
OL,14,Fstage where heating demand is falling,
OL,15,Fand gas storage levels in Europe are
OL,16,Falready relatively low."
OL,18,FIn the UK, household energy bills are
OL,19,Fpartly shielded by the price cap set
OL,20,Fevery three months by the regulator,
OL,21,FOfgem.
OL,26,@oD@BpmoD@[pnpD@RO]tD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772528658
OL,3,CQatar gas shutdown sends market price
OL,4,Csurging and could impact UK energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FLast week, it was announced that the
OL,8,Faverage annual bill will fall by #117
OL,9,Ffrom April, largely because the
OL,10,Fgovernment has decided to move the
OL,11,Fcost of energy efficiency schemes from
OL,12,Fconsumer bills to general taxation.
OL,14,FBut that could change again if
OL,15,Fwholesale gas prices stay high.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772528658
OL,3,CQatar gas shutdown sends market price
OL,4,Csurging and could impact UK energy
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FAs a rough guide, if the market price
OL,8,Fremains at the levels reached today
OL,9,Ffor the next three months - and it may
OL,10,Fnot - the typical household bill could
OL,11,Frise by around #150 a year when the
OL,12,Fcap is reset in July.
OL,14,FIn other words, events in the Gulf
OL,15,Ftonight could still end up showing up
OL,16,Fon energy bills in Britain this
OL,17,Fsummer. If the disruption persists.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
